dialogue 1.text: I know this is your jam ! Jam is good with peanut butter :D

Dear Fallon, 
 2017 has been quite an interesting year for both of us. Though everything has not always been easy, I feel that we have learned so much together, and that we have found a way to turn the scary rolleroaster of life into something that we can understand and appreciate.

dialogue 2.text: Your passion and curiosity has rubbed off on me, and I really feel that I can be myself around you. Thank you for being there with me, I'm very happy to have you in my life ! May we keep supporting each other for the year to come!

dialogue 3.text:
Merry Christmas, 
 Happy New Years, 
 and to a bright future! 
 Your lover and boyfriend, 
 Yanik
